{"tid":438780,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"有證據嘅陰謀論/外星人post","createTime":"2017-10-17T08:54:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-25T13:46:47.000Z","uid":61050,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ec589b6fca8dbc348f5a9b6d787b398cd4e21919","tid":438780,"uid":61050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T08:54:37.000Z","msg":"之前有睇開外星人post 最近開始睇多咗陰謀論嘅嘢 <br />\n發覺好多陰謀論文章係就係有好多疑似係證據嘅野 不過多數好亂 <br />\n有時仲有好多唔關事嘅證據攞嚟煲大個linkage誇張化添 <br />\n所以啲人唔信陰謀論我都明嘅<br />\n<br />\n所以我想係度拋磚引玉 整理一下我睇過而又返啲證據嘅陰謀論 <br />\n引你哋入嚟講吓陰謀論/外星人(因為我都想知多啲外星人嘅嘢)<br />\n<br />\n嗱 我而家唔係逼你信 亦都唔係要你信到十足十 信唔信係個人決定 <br />\n你地自己理性分析下啲資料啦吓 (頭盔已戴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 瑞士Gotthard Base Tunnel開幕禮<br />\n<br />\n你正正常常起完條公營隧道 個開幕禮都係不外乎都係剪絲帶啊 表演啊咁 開心野黎嘅咪賀一賀佢囉 <br />\n會唔會有人好似瑞士政府咁 搞到成個開幕禮好似邪教儀式咁? <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zW5gklIKcDg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzW5gklIKcDg&d=CioNDxIeEkIf5bMV6of9kttKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=be793391\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zW5gklIKcDg</a><br />\n成個開幕典禮表演都好邪教feel <br />\n有無人講吓成個表演象徵左啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n27:25 見到德國總理Angela Merkel同法國總統Francois Hollande都有去到開幕禮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n都有主流媒體報道話呢個開幕禮好奇怪<br />\nBBC<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/news/in-pictures-36428799\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fin-pictures-36428799&d=CioNDxIeEkIf5bMV6of9kttKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=54bda278\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fin-pictures-36428799&h=b77a71d4\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bbc.com/news/in-pictures-36428799</a><br />\n又講到意大利領袖都有去<br />\n<br />\nThe Daily Mail <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3620446/A-winged-baby-semi-naked-dancers-man-bird-s-nest-head-Switzerland-decided-mark-opening-world-s-longest-rail-tunnel.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-3620446%2FA-winged-baby-semi-naked-dancers-man-bird-s-nest-head-Switzerland-decided-mark-opening-world-s-longest-rail-tunnel.html&d=CioNDxIeEkIf5bMV6of9kttKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=fb95a103\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3620446/A-winged-baby-semi-naked-dancers-man-bird-s-nest-head-Switzerland-decided-mark-opening-world-s-longest-rail-tunnel.html</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 係冇第二嘅 對我嚟講已經打咗好多字啦 得閒再打 你地都講下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3080d5620538e9834090c45c277aa2f4fa71fc1","tid":438780,"uid":61050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T09:14:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c23b827b718b717689de9f1674e3c4e182cb4015","tid":438780,"uid":13703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T09:19:49.000Z","msg":"las vegas 槍擊案唔止一個槍手+唔止一度槍擊?"},{"pid":"05a13a2dbf88547b909a5df719a2c7435596cc7d","tid":438780,"uid":61050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T09:21:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>las vegas 槍擊案唔止一個槍手+唔止一度槍擊?</blockquote><br />\n好多人咁講 又話咩公開"},{"pid":"a891cc56ccd151de4dadd59a24ba1b2a14b4217f","tid":438780,"uid":61050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T09:32:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>las vegas 槍擊案唔止一個槍手+唔止一度槍擊?</blockquote><br />\n好多人咁講 又話咩公開講話有多過一個槍手嘅目擊者唔去失咗蹤 就係啱啱死咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 唔知詳情</blockquote>"},{"pid":"0025053ef78aaecad45c210bcbcbfa68e8a12cbb","tid":438780,"uid":61050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T09:34:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59b2a21b68a3d37ad78a615fd6638a9d8ab14f6b","tid":438780,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,